name: "Theodore and the nymph" detail
description:
"Theodore and the nymph" detail taken from the entire work.
Digital images taken from the original oil and permanent ink painting made by Alison Williams in 2017. One is the work in its entirety and the other is a detail. An awareness of sexual deviance and the monstrosities that mankind is capable of. The actual painting is 77cm x 55.5cm and will be made available as a collection item at a later stage.
